HEADWORD: Pig-jawed
<hw>Pig"-jawed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Having the upper jaw projecting beyond the lower, with the upper
incisors in advance of the lower; -- said of dogs.</def>⟦br⟧
